      One important aspect of React to get an understanding of early on is the differences between what is referred to as functional or "Stateless Function", and a React class component. The basic difference is easy to explain, a functional component has no State associated with it. These are the basic objects we worked with extensively in javascript before starting to learn React. 
   
    </p>
